---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Hogg Country" description="Jimmy Hogg ‚Äî Triple O Crowner, Sassafras Award recipient, and 2026 AT NOBO thru-hiker.">
  <section class="about-page">
    <div class="container">
      <header class="about-header">
        <div class="badge-row">
          <span class="badge">Triple O Crowner</span>
          <span class="badge accent">Sassafras Award</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="font-display">Jimmy Hogg</h1>
        <p class="subtitle hand">Arkansas hiker. 2026 AT NOBO.</p>
      </header>

      <div class="about-content">
        <section class="bio-section">
          <h2>The Trail So Far</h2>
          <p>
            I'm an avid long-distance hiker from Arkansas with over 840 miles of thru-hiking experience across three major trail systems. In 2026, I'm taking on the Appalachian Trail ‚Äî 2,197.9 miles from Springer Mountain, Georgia to Mount Katahdin, Maine.
          </p>
          <p>
            This site documents my journey: past adventures, current preparation, and the complete field guide I've built for the AT.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="stats-section">
          <h2>Hiking Resume</h2>

          <div class="thru-hikes">
            <h3>Completed Thru-Hikes</h3>
            <div class="hike-cards">
              <div class="hike-card">
                <span class="hike-name">Ouachita Trail</span>
                <span class="hike-stats">~223 mi / ~45,000 ft</span>
                <span class="hike-location">Arkansas-Oklahoma</span>
              </div>
              <div class="hike-card">
                <span class="hike-name">Ozark Highlands Trail</span>
                <span class="hike-stats">~270 mi / ~35,000 ft</span>
                <span class="hike-location">Northern Arkansas</span>
              </div>
              <div class="hike-card">
                <span class="hike-name">Ozark Trail</span>
                <span class="hike-stats">~230 mi / ~40,000 ft</span>
                <span class="hike-location">Missouri</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="totals">
            <div class="total-stat">
              <span class="total-value">840+</span>
              <span class="total-label">Miles Completed</span>
            </div>
            <div class="total-stat">
              <span class="total-value">120k+</span>
              <span class="total-label">Feet of Elevation</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="recognition-section">
          <h2>Recognition</h2>
          <div class="award-card">
            <div class="award-icon">üèÜ</div>
            <div class="award-info">
              <h3>Sassafras Award ‚Äî Ozark Society</h3>
              <p>Awarded for completion of the Ouachita Trail, Ozark Highlands Trail, and Ozark Trail.</p>
              <p class="award-note"><em>6th person in history to receive this award.</em></p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="at-section">
          <h2>Prior AT Experience</h2>
          <ul class="at-list">
            <li>
              <strong>Standing Bear Farm to Hot Springs, NC</strong>
              <span>~35 miles | ~9,000 ft elevation gain | Full pack, winter conditions</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Newfound Gap to Kuwohi (Overnight)</strong>
              <span>~16 miles RT | ~3,300 ft gain | Shelter stay in ~17¬∞F | Summit: 6,643 ft</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p class="at-total"><strong>Total AT Miles:</strong> ~49 miles of hard winter terrain</p>
        </section>

        <section class="next-section">
          <h2>What's Next</h2>
          <p>
            February 2026: Springer Mountain. The full Appalachian Trail, northbound. Follow along through the <a href="/">trail log</a>, explore the <a href="/guide">Field Guide</a>, or check out the <a href="/tools">planning tools</a> I've built for the journey.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .about-page {
      padding: 3rem 0 5rem;
    }

    .about-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      padding-bottom: 2rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .badge-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
      background: rgba(166, 181, 137, 0.2);
      border: 1px solid var(--alpine);
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--pine);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }

    .badge.accent {
      background: rgba(240, 224, 0, 0.2);
      border-color: var(--marker);
      color: #8a7800;
    }

    .about-header h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 3.5rem);
      margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
      color: var(--ink);
    }

    .subtitle {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin: 0;
    }

    .about-content {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .about-content section {
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .about-content h2 {
      font-family: Oswald, sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      color: var(--pine);
      margin: 0 0 1rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }

    .about-content p {
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin: 0 0 1rem;
    }

    .about-content a {
      color: var(--pine);
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .about-content a:hover {
      color: var(--terra);
    }

    /* Thru-hike cards */
    .hike-cards {
      display: grid;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .hike-card {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: baseline;
      padding: 1rem;
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .hike-name {
      font-family: Oswald, sans-serif;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--ink);
    }

    .hike-stats {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--pine);
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .hike-location {
      width: 100%;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    /* Totals */
    .totals {
      display: flex;
      gap: 2rem;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      background: rgba(166, 181, 137, 0.1);
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .total-stat {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .total-value {
      display: block;
      font-family: Oswald, sans-serif;
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--pine);
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .total-label {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    /* Award card */
    .award-card {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      padding: 1.25rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(240, 224, 0, 0.1), rgba(240, 224, 0, 0.05));
      border: 1px solid rgba(240, 224, 0, 0.3);
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .award-icon {
      font-size: 2rem;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .award-info h3 {
      font-family: Oswald, sans-serif;
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
      color: var(--ink);
    }

    .award-info p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .award-note {
      margin-top: 0.5rem !important;
      color: var(--pine) !important;
    }

    /* AT list */
    .at-list {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0 0 1rem;
    }

    .at-list li {
      padding: 0.75rem 0;
      border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--border);
    }

    .at-list li:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    .at-list strong {
      display: block;
      color: var(--ink);
      margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }

    .at-list span {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .at-total {
      padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
      background: rgba(77, 89, 74, 0.1);
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .at-total strong {
      color: var(--pine);
    }

    /* Next section */
    .next-section {
      padding-top: 1.5rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .totals {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }

      .hike-card {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }

      .hike-stats {
        order: 1;
      }
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
